{{Mission Description|type=adventure|location=Central Starskiff Haven|update|Tantan mentions that the Palace of Astrum had extracted very important data from the cycranes at the intersection. Combined with the on-site witness testimony, it might pinpoint the whereabouts of the starskiff that caused the accident.}}
